Analysis and visualization of Indian Premeir League(IPL)¶

Investigation overview¶

In this Investigation, i wanted to look at the features of players that could be used to predict the player performances. The main focus was on the features like 'Batsman', 'Batsman_runs', 'Bowler', 'Player_dismissed' from delivery data and features like 'winner' and 'player_of_match' from matches data

Dataset Overview¶

The data sets delivery and matches consists of 15460 ball by ball data and 636 matches with attributes include'Batting_team', 'Bowling_team', 'Season' and 'winner'. Few of these attributes are used for the analysis and visualization

Analysis and Visualization¶

The first Visualization shows the teams that won the more matches in IPL. It is clear that Mumbai Indians(MI) has more winning percentage of all the teams played in IPL whereas Kings eleven punjab (KTK) has least winning percentage

The second Visualization shows the man of the match in IPL. It is evident that player named Chris Gayle has 18 man of the match awards followed by 16 ,15 by Yk Pathan and DA Warner, AB Devilliers. Man of the match describes its "one man show" in a team that contributed more for team winning

The Third visualization shows the top 15 batsman in the IPL. Sk Raina tops the list with more than 4500 runs scored and V kohli followed by second and RG sharma third respectively. This analysis helps to look that these players are helpful in making their team winning by scoring high runs

In this visualization, two top batsman named Dhoni and Kohli are compared to each other with highest number of 4's and 6's in IPL. This comparision helps when team required 15 runs in 6 balls then there is a probability that these players take their team winning side

It is evident that player named V Kohli had good statistics throught out the IPL seasons except the season 2017 where as players are consistent about their performances. David warner has also seen to be well played in IPL.

When it comes to Batting performances in death(last 5 overs to be called) teams like MI and RCB finished scoring high runs when compared to other teams

From this visualization, we can see the top individual scored by batsman in IPL. Chris Gayle tops the list with 175 runs and scored more than 5 hundreds where as shikar dhawan, Ms dhoni , Goutham gambhir never scored a century (100 runs)

This bar graph shows the top 15 bowlers in IPL. Malinga picked more than 150 plus wickets. we can estimate that he can defend the situation where 8 runs required in 6 balls and make their team winning

Here is an great visualization that shows the top ten bowlers in IPL. Of course again malinga tops the list but there is economy(It is number of runs conceeded in over like less economy means great bowler and more economy means easy to play) who has less than 6.5 where it becomes to difficult play in R Ashwin over. whereas player named Vinay kumar has high economy 8 (easy to play) but he picked the wickets as well

Key Insights¶

Indian premier league is a T-20 format cricket League which is played every year in India since 2008. The management of 8 different teams, auction the players to make a good team.Player Analysis(Batting and Bowling) help franchises, sponsors, cricket selectors and cricket-boards of different countries to make a good team prediction. They rely on player analysis for good decision making in team, which player to be auctioned, and at what price the player to be auctioned. Sponsors for advertising their products prefer player analysis and pick a player at the beginning stage of his career, which helps them in future for the endorsements . Cricket team selection committees also prefer player analysis to make the probable eleven key players for the upcoming series and major league tournaments. I have learned player analysis in cricket is very important for making decisions in player selection, franchises to auction and make a team, sponsors for their endorsements, Team Managements for picking best eleven players. These analysis are helpful to selectors where they can pick the best eleven players that includes Batsman and Bowlers.
